159
00:15:30,450 --> 00:15:31,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala Center Kang,
semuanya baik-baik saja?</font>

160
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:33,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami sudah menangkap basah Mo Tae Gu.
Kirim tim bantuan kesini.</font>

161
00:15:33,490 --> 00:15:35,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami berada di 190 Pantai Sungwun.</font>

162
00:15:35,090 --> 00:15:36,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Detektif Shim terluka serius,</font>

163
00:15:36,690 --> 00:15:38,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan Detektif Moo sedang
melawan Mo Tae Gu.</font>

164
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:41,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Code Zero. Lokasi, 190
Pantai Sungwun, Sungwun-dong.</font>

165
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:42,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Personil patroli dan tim paramedis,
harap segera ke TKP.</font>

166
00:15:42,620 --> 00:15:44,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Tersangkanya adalah Mo Tae Gu. Dia
berusaha membunuh Detektif Shim...,</font>

167
00:15:44,650 --> 00:15:47,110
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan Detektif Moo saat ini
sedang berjuang melawannya.</font>

168
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:10,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi ini tempatnya?</font>

169
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:14,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini taman bermainmu?</font>

170
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:16,850
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Demi menutupi
kenyataan pahitmu ini...,</i></font>

171
00:16:16,850 --> 00:16:19,650
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau membunuh istriku, bangsat.</font>

172
00:16:19,650 --> 00:16:22,350
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Hari ini, kau akan mati di tanganku.
Camkan itu.</i></font>

173
